      "title": "gittern<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>类似吉他的古老有线乐器，14世纪晚期，来自古法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">guiterne</i>，源自拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cithara</i>，源自希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kithara</i>（参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of guitar \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/guitar\">guitar</a>）。</p>"
