    {
      "title": "sitar<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>长颈弦乐器，印度音乐器乐，1845年，源自印地语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sitar</i>，来自波斯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sitar</i> “三弦”，源自 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">si</i> “三”（古波斯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">thri-</i>； 参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of three \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/three\">three</a>）+ <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">tar</i> “弦”（源自 PIE 词根 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *ten- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/*ten-\">*ten-</a> “拉伸”）。相关： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Sitarist</i>。</p>"
